{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1cb89db6ba","title":"给冯元春的信","origin":"《四川省右派言论选集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月20日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c4b0ada8b","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"1cb89db6ba"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2fe7ce1102","name":"四川医学院"},{"id":"5cdea653bf","name":"“北京来蓉社”"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"29937c9b5e","type":"title","text":"给冯元春的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"9535d0f4ff","type":"authors","text":"四川医学院“北京来蓉社”","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"cb70c1c436","type":"subtitle","text":"(原编者注：发信地点只注：四川医学院寄)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"271a1a3450","type":"appellation","text":"冯元春同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"3bc60dffa8","type":"paragraph","text":"我们派代表听了你的发言，均表示拥护和支持，希望你勇敢坚持真理，思想上更应该沉着应战。根据近来两天各大专学校的情况，起码有二分之一以上的知识青年是支持你的革命理论，因为处处都是结合实际，目前有部分人要求你答辩，今天趁此机会再供给你一些材料如下：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"e2bab14133","type":"paragraph","text":"C.C.P出卖中华民族利益","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"34ee204d1a","type":"paragraph","text":"事实——在全国行施土改中，向地主斗争出来的金银，他们全部运到苏联去了，这是经济方面的问题。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"668dd57c8d","type":"paragraph","text":"人民军队内部，包括陆海空军，都是苏联军事人员操纵，这是这事方面的问题。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"d210acd9f5","type":"paragraph","text":"从幼儿教育一直到高等教育，不但全学苏联，并且把青年送往苏联，最典型的是叫“一边倒”，这是教育方面的问题。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"ba31ec52fd","type":"paragraph","text":"结论：中国的财政、军事、教育全操纵在苏联手里，甚至于人民的衣、食、住、行都要苏联化，此乃说明中华民族的利益全为C.C.P出卖了。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"329a17d9fb","type":"paragraph","text":"以上事实是全国人民知道。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"0aa4463098","type":"paragraph","text":"其次是旅顺大连口更为显著，同时那些事实，大部分我们搞有照片，有些被压迫人民的诉苦(农民)也有录音片子，假使四川日报和成都日报能够将你的发言发表的话，我们决定供给你具体照片作证，希望你大胆地进行“答辩”，他们不敢用敌对手段对付你，目前全国各地轰轰烈烈地向C.C.P进行无情地斗争，放心吧！","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"77c21f08f2","type":"paragraph","text":"北京来蓉社","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"877ee7ba72","type":"paragraph","text":"上海情报分社　联合西南办事处启","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"},{"id":"42c6780748","type":"paragraph","text":"营救高饶会","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba"}],"page":{"id":"77af11a8db","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cb89db6ba","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}